snippet.textDisplay: The concept is so nice, and unfortunately has become a harsh reality for many families. As far as him singing, I can’t lie and say that I’m blown away. My opinion “he can carry a tune, but average is the nicest Thing I can say regarding him vocally”. I watch these shows, and it drives me crazy that people like *“Leroy Sanchez “Connard Maynard“ or “Alex Aiono” ** are never on it! I’m sorry, but all three of those guys could win the voice, American Idol, America’s got talent, and any other show with laryngitis! That’s how talented those three people are… If you don’t know who they are, do yourself a favor and copy and paste each one of their names one at a time. None of those three guys as far as I’m concerned are famous, or are “ household names” like they should be! If I ever won the Powerball, signing all three of those guys would be one of the first things I did! Justin Bieber and Shawn Mendes would have stiff competition if those three guys had the name/fame as they do. Shawn did come along way, he earned every bit of it. Not to say that Justin didn’t, he was going to be famous no matter what… His career started pretty much the same time that YouTube did, and all of those young girls were never going to let him not become famous! Regardless, he has a phenomenal talent… Check out those three guys though if you do not know who they are. Let me know if you think I’m crazy…
